name: 【Concept】Carried Breast Rest 托物歇胸
description:
If what you want is "Breast on Tray lora", sorry this one is different.

Accroding to my test, things the girl can carry contain: book stack, cardboard box, gift box

Oh, watermelon can also be carried, but the output is not very stable as the watermelon may be not round enough🤣 And the breasts may not rest ideally.

Remember to make the breasts big enough! Thank you Kashino chan(

如果你想要托盘上的胸lora，很抱歉这个是不一样的。

根据我的测试，姑娘能拿着的东西包括：book stack（书堆）, cardboard box（纸箱）, gift box（礼物盒子）

哦对了，watermelon（西瓜）也能托着，但是结果不是很稳定，这个瓜可能不够圆🤣胸可能也托得不够理想。

记得让胸足够大！谢谢你樫野酱（
